    "type": "message",
    "text": "Here's how things were for a year until a month ago. An infinite surface on which you could move definitions around independently.\n\nThe problem: sometimes definitions would overlap. And I was wary of going down the slippery slope of a complete overlapping window manager just to solve this one problem.",
