        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "On Dec 10, after some prototyping on Lua Carousel, I gave my definitions some minimal physics so they could nudge other definitions aside.\n\nThe problem I quickly ran into was: it was very hard to move one definition to the other side of another. More broadly, my heretofore calm UI --  where things mostly stayed in place until you move them -- became much more chaotic."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
